## My Recommendation
```
Grid hashing for production:
✅ Strict — no chaining possible by design
✅ O(n) — 1M rows in < 1 second  
✅ Deterministic — same input always gives same output
✅ Simple — 10 lines of code, no dependencies
⚠️ Boundary effect — acceptable tradeoff
